ssed=\r\n) etc etc and at the other extreme this layer can, if properly\n channalized=\r\n as is done in genuine Vaishava Bhakti, it can make one experience Divine A=\r\nnanda and manifest the &quot;antaratmah&quot; as an unfailing guide to the path.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;=\r\nBR&gt;In a nutshell, a genuine &quot;experience&quot; is good and authentic only to the =\r\nextent that it helps to modify and transform your waking surface personalit=\r\ny. That is the only true test. Rest all the range of experiences that come =\r\nfrom this realm, and 95 percent of Yogis get experiences ONLY from this rea=\r\nlm, are just sound and fury without substance. &lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;In the writings of S=\r\nri Aurobindo, he calls it the intermediate zone, which has destroyed innume=\r\nrable yogis who have got swept away by the light and sound of this realm. O=\r\nne sure-shot way to cross this realm, and all sadhakas will have to cross t=\r\nhis some day, is to hang on tightly to the fundamentals.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;-Regards&lt;BR=\r\n&gt;&nbsp;Rajarshi &lt;BR&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;I&gt;&lt;B&gt;\n&lt;DIV class=3Dyiv1759129612=\r\nMsoNormal&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE: 16px&quot; class=3Dyiv1759129612Apple-sty=\r\nle-span&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;COLOR: rgb(153,153,153)&quot; class=3Dyiv1759129612App=\r\nle-style-span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY: times new r=\r\noman, new york, times, serif&quot; class=3Dyiv1759129612yui_3_2_0_2_134243527249=\r\n950&gt;awaktam wyaktimApannam manyantE mAmabuddhayah |&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;SPAN styl=\r\ne=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: navy; FONT-SIZE: 10pt&quot; class=3D&quot;yiv175912=\r\n9612yui_3_2_0_2_134243506227946 yiv1759129612yui_3_2_0_2_134243527249952 yi=\r\nv1759129612yui_3_2_0_37_134976159846786&quot;&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 face=3D&quot;Time=\r\ns New Roman&quot;&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;param bhAwamaj